","count":1},{"word":"usually","count":1},{"word":"tells","count":1},{"word":"things","count":1},{"word":"though","count":1},{"word":"focusing","count":1},{"word":"today's","count":1},{"word":"definitely","count":1},{"word":"direction","count":1},{"word":"earlier","count":1},{"word":"resources","count":1},{"word":"short","count":1},{"word":"sums","count":1},{"word":"felt","count":1},{"word":"sentences","count":1},{"word":"longer","count":1},{"word":"detailed","count":1},{"word":"weird","count":1},{"word":"plus","count":1},{"word":"lower","count":1},{"word":"left","count":1},{"word":"true","count":1},{"word":"anywhere","count":1},{"word":"rest","count":1},{"word":"either","count":1},{"word":"done","count":1},{"word":"starts","count":1},{"word":"saying","count":1},{"word":"dream","count":1},{"word":"recorded","count":1},{"word":"move","count":1},{"word":"next","count":1},{"word":"step","count":1},{"word":"instructions","count":1},{"word":"graph","count":1},{"word":"indicates","count":1},{"word":"reconfigure","count":1},{"word":"console","count":1},{"word":"someone","count":1},{"word":"first","count":1},{"word":"big","count":1},{"word":"sister","count":1},{"word":"verification","count":1},{"word":"required","count":1},{"word":"argument","count":1},{"word":"information","count":1},{"word":"passcode","count":1},{"word":"nothing","count":1},{"word":"else","count":1},{"word":"works","count":1},{"word":"maybe","count":1},{"word":"try","count":1},{"word":"guessing","count":1},{"word":"fighting","count":1},{"word":"old","count":1},{"word":"man","count":1},{"word":"gets","count":1},{"word":"around","count":1},{"word":"three","count":1},{"word":"different","count":1},{"word":"areas","count":1},{"word":"idea","count":1},{"word":"two","count":1},{"word":"sound","count":1},{"word":"cool","count":1},{"word":"overlapping","count":1},{"word":"area","count":1},{"word":"small","count":1},{"word":"corner","count":1},{"word":"upper","count":1},{"word":"living","count":1},{"word":"quarter","count":1},{"word":"finally","count":1},{"word":"everyone's","count":1},{"word":"looking","count":1},{"word":"great","count":1},{"word":"remembers","count":1},{"word":"eating","count":1},{"word":"alone","count":1},{"word":"always","count":1},{"word":"lonely","count":1},{"word":"wonder","count":1},{"word":"seems","count":1},{"word":"lost","count":1},{"word":"fixed","count":1},{"word":"issue","count":1},{"word":"anyway","count":1},{"word":"guest","count":1},{"word":"ministry","count":1},{"word":"promised","count":1},{"word":"mister","count":1},{"word":"lady","count":1},{"word":"beside","count":1},{"word":"strange","count":1},{"word":"kind","count":1},{"word":"late","count":1},{"word":"modee","count":1},{"word":"said","count":1},{"word":"tested","count":1},{"word":"another","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Stop, stop. English, please. Whatever, something about power supply, right? I know who to turn to. Follow me.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"What are you talking about, Uncle Lei'li? My brother asked me to work with {PlayerName} to reboot the Refinery Tower.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Yes, rebooting the Refinery Tower requires sufficient power. Uncle Lei'li, you know the best about the power equipment. What's your advice?","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"...Hm, so it is...","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"I'm not snooping! I just thought of a really smart way to find Grandpa Hong.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"I read a story once about a detective who didn't talk much, and his friend, a doctor, helped him solve all sorts of mysteries.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"The detective would sometimes look at the bad guy's past to find clues.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"After all, a person's past usually tells you why they do things now!","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"That's why I think though focusing on today's entry is definitely the right direction, earlier entries are still important resources.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Hee hee. Now you know!","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Most of his entries are pretty short. He just sums up his day and how he felt in a few sentences.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"But I did find some longer, more detailed entries. I think they're important, like this one.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"What's your take? Doesn't this story feel weird?","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"I feel the same. Plus, the lower half of the page is left blank.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"True. It's like the story doesn’t really go anywhere, and the rest of the page is just blank.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Either way, this story feels like it's only half done.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"You know, it starts by saying it's a dream being recorded. Could that be why it feels this way?","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Right. Let's move on to the next step of the instructions.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"The graph indicates that we have to reconfigure the Refinery Tower with the console.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Let's find someone to talk to first.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Big {Male=brother;Female=sister}, is this what we should do?","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"A verification is required...","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"The entry is mostly about an argument with a researcher. No information about a passcode.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"If nothing else works, maybe we'll just have to try guessing...","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"You, you... Aren't you that researcher who was fighting with Grandpa Hong, in the journal?","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"For an old man, he sure gets around! But looks like it's mostly just three different areas.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"No idea what you two are talking about, but you sure sound smart. You're pretty cool, {PlayerName}!","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"The overlapping area is a small corner in the upper living quarter. Let's go take a look!","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Look, {PlayerName}. That's Grandpa Hong.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"We finally found you, Grandpa Hong. Everyone's been looking for you.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Great. Grandpa Hong remembers me.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Eating alone always feels a bit lonely. No wonder Grandpa Hong seems so down.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Grandpa Hong...","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Right. Grandpa Hong, we found your lost journal, and fixed the reboot issue of the Refinery Tower.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Anyway, the guest from the Ministry is here with the samples like they promised. That's this {Male=mister;Female=lady} beside me.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Grandpa Hong still looks a bit strange. Let's take him to my brother.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"It's kind of late now, {PlayerName}. Like Uncle Modee said, the samples can't be tested as of now. Why don't you come here another day?","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003}]}